            since 2014.  Robert has been recognized as one of North Alabama's premier Home Inspectors and has 
            been awarded the title of Certified Inspector by ASHI.​</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-size" style="padding:0px 2px 0px 2px">
        <p style="font-style:italic; font-weight:bolder">"Every home inspected, whether it be brand new or 
